Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退了  阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burst射擊完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子  開始填充
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種物量…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反應得太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰開始2小時了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.61,0:11:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照計劃B2的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames和Kyrios應該快到匯合地點了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果GN Arms能用的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按時間算  應該從B2改為E5
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣的話  那台機體會來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:35.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭  頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了  超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超兵？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前遇到的人革聯的專用機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵機接近  敵機接近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:28.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正中了下懷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞  充填還要多少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有170
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太長了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:12:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你叫啥名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通訊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:11.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是超兵1號——蘇摩·佩麗絲少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇摩·佩麗絲啊  好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得殺掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫且離開  少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.13,0:13:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  真沒勁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面就交給你了  阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.66,0:13:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里路亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從戰鬥開始已經過了5小時了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:13:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去聽聽其它監視者們的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的任務或許到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人真讓人討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第7MS部隊  到活動極限時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓第16MS部隊頂上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:33.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要出場了  少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去做出擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要持續到什麼時候啊  這種攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要讓人吃個飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能交出Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.35,0:15:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over Flag隊  任務時間到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉哈姆·艾卡  要出擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯絡各機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的目標是龐然大物Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在停止炮擊的同時開始進行捕獲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別撞上的敵人的光束哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從戰鬥開始起已經過了15個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…怎麼了  炮擊停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:21.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦喲  怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行動太遲鈍了  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住Gundam了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校  抓住長翅膀的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意點  少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會像上次那樣突然動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮官  確認目標
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over Flag
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以E陣型開始執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長  約修亞他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約修亞  不要打亂陣型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副隊長的派頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中變形！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還以為這是屬於自己的專利嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:17:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約修亞他…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  改為C陣型
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指尖的感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想緊緊抱著你啊  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像是睡美人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特  有沒有來自Meister的聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:32.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:44.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Meister的生命  在逐漸消失…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的Meister們…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在3點方向有敵人的影子！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MA？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台Enact…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該把之前欠的還回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  Gundam啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別就這麼掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.94,0:19:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣啊  Agurisa的等離子場的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.09,0:19:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別光留下機體消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克魯吉斯的毛頭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外交部收到了非正式的訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在歐亞大陸進行的聯合演習中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.59,0:20:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being好像出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙方好像已進入了交戰狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  居然只用4台Gundam來挑戰近1000台的MS部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本是太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.31,0:20:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.75,0:20:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  這個世界扭曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神的原因  還是人的原因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧  那時…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這扭曲的世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在成不了任何東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不斷失去的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:23.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gun…dam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gun…dam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gun…dam
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gun…dam
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gun…dam！！
