Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.80,0:23:12.91,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}As life goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.24,0:23:18.35,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}忘れちゃいけないからYeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:23.57,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Don't let it go...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.91,0:23:30.90,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}この広い大地の仲間たちのこと
